Content-Type: application/json

### Test Get Invoices List - With Room Filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/invoices?month=3&year=2026&roomId=69b581e660c3ad535c71695d
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Get Invoices List - With Status Filter
